data.description: Great investment opportunity! Occupied unit is currently under market rent, but on a month to month lease. Vacant half of the duplex has new carpet, new baseboards, new paint and texture, new interior doors, updated fixtures, and a new garbage disposal. Both units can take advantage of the new backyard fence.
